%main.single-page__body
  %section.single-page__body__container
    %h2.single-page__body__title
      会員情報入力
    -# サーバサイドで新規登録実装時、form以下はform-forに変更のこと
    %form.single-page__body__form
      .single-page__body__form__box
        .single-page__body__form__group.single-page__body__form__group--top
          %label{for: 'nickname', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__label'}
            ニックネーム
          %span.single-page__body__form__group__require-mark
            必須
          %input{type: 'text', name: 'nickname', placeholder: '例) メルカリ太郎', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__input-text'}
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %label{for: 'email', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__label'}
            メールアドレス
          %span.single-page__body__form__group__require-mark
            必須
          %input{type: 'email', name: 'email', placeholder: 'PC・携帯どちらでも可', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__input-text'}
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %label{for: 'password', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__label'}
            パスワード
          %span.single-page__body__form__group__require-mark
            必須
          %input{type: 'password', name: 'password', placeholder: '6文字以上', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__input-text'}
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %label{for: 'password', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__label'}
            パスワード（確認）
          %span.single-page__body__form__group__require-mark
            必須
          %input{type: 'password', name: 'password2', placeholder: '6文字以上', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__input-text'}
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %h3.single-page__body__form__group__title
            本人確認
          %p.single-page__body__form__group__text
            安心・安全にご利用いただくために、お客さまの本人情報の登録にご協力ください。他のお客さまに公開されることはありません。
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %label{for: 'family_name', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__label'}
            姓（全角）
          %span.single-page__body__form__group__require-mark
            必須
          %input{type: 'text', name: 'family_name', placeholder: '例) 山田', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__input-text'}
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %label{for: 'first_name', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__label'}
            名（全角）
          %span.single-page__body__form__group__require-mark
            必須
          %input{type: 'text', name: 'first_name', placeholder: '例) 彩', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__input-text'}
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %label{for: 'family_name', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__label'}
            姓カナ（全角）
          %span.single-page__body__form__group__require-mark
            必須
          %input{type: 'text', name: 'family_name', placeholder: '例) ヤマダ', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__input-text'}
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %label{for: 'first_name_kana', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__label'}
            名カナ（全角）
          %span.single-page__body__form__group__require-mark
            必須
          %input{type: 'text', name: 'first_name_kana', placeholder: '例) アヤ', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__input-text'}
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %label{for: 'birthday', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__label'}
            生年月日
          %span.single-page__body__form__group__require-mark
            必須
          %br
          .single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap
            .single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap
              %select{name: 'year', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select'}
                %option{value: '', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select__option'}
                  '--'
                %option{value: '2019', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select__option'}
                  '2019'
                %option{value: '2018', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select__option'}
                  '2018'
              = fa_icon 'angle-down', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__icon-arrow-bottom'
            %span.single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__unit-text
              年
            .single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap
              %select{name: 'month', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select'}
                %option{value: '', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select__option'}
                  '--'
                %option{value: '12', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select__option'}
                  '12'
                %option{value: '11', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select__option'}
                  '11'
              = fa_icon 'angle-down', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__icon-arrow-bottom'
            %span.single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__unit-text
              月
            .single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap
              %select{name: 'day', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select'}
                %option{value: '', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select__option'}
                  '--'
                %option{value: '31', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select__option'}
                  '31'
                %option{value: '30', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__select__option'}
                  '30'
              = fa_icon 'angle-down', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__select-wrap__icon-arrow-bottom'
            %span.single-page__body__form__group__birthday-select-wrap__unit-text
              日
        %p.single-page__body__form__info-text
          ※ 本人情報は正しく入力してください。会員登録後、修正するにはお時間を頂く場合があります。
      .single-page__body__form__box
        .single-page__body__form__group
          -# 「私はロボットではありません」は実装方法後で調べて作る。今は画像を仮置きで置く
          .single-page__body__form__group__recaptcha
            = image_tag('recaptcha.jpeg', size: "304x78", alt: "recaptcha")
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %p.single-page__body__form__group__text.single-page__body__form__group__text--text-center
            「次へ進む」のボタンを押すことにより、
            %a.single-page__body__form__group__text__link
              利用規約
            に同意したものとみなします
        %button.single-page__body__form__submit-btn
          次へ進む
        .single-page__body__form__group
          %p.single-page__body__form__group__text.single-page__body__form__group__text--text-right
            %a.single-page__body__form__group__text__link
              本人情報の登録について
            = fa_icon 'angle-right', class: 'single-page__body__form__group__text__icon-arrow-right'
